WEBVTT

00:00.105 --> 00:02.672
[Gun cocks]Morgan Jones?

00:02.716 --> 00:03.934
How do you know
that name?

00:03.978 --> 00:05.110
Victor told us
all about you.

00:05.153 --> 00:06.546
Victor's alive?

00:06.589 --> 00:08.374
I gave up my family
to put this guy away.

00:08.417 --> 00:09.940
I'm not about to let him
succeed now.

00:09.984 --> 00:11.812
Recognize this voice, Teddy?
Give you a hint.

00:11.855 --> 00:14.162
Last time you heard it, you were
in a Denton County courthouse

00:14.206 --> 00:16.077
listening to my testimony
against you.

00:16.121 --> 00:19.167
Couldn't kill me then,
and you sure as shit
aren't gonna do it now.

00:19.211 --> 00:20.908
[ Gun cocks ]Step away from
the girl, Teddy.

00:20.951 --> 00:22.083
Not fixin' to hurt ya.

00:22.127 --> 00:24.259
[Rumbling]

00:24.303 --> 00:27.958
♪

00:28.002 --> 00:28.916
Aah!

00:42.886 --> 00:46.151
[Static]

00:53.375 --> 00:56.726
[Dishes clinking]

01:01.644 --> 01:04.995
[Inhales deeply]

