02:37.305 --> 02:39.089
It's us again.

02:39.133 --> 02:41.135
John Francis Dorie V

02:41.179 --> 02:44.921
and my daughter-in-law,
June Dorie.

02:44.965 --> 02:46.880
The two folks 6 feet under.

02:46.923 --> 02:48.664
Very much alive, though.

02:48.708 --> 02:50.536
Plenty of food.

02:50.579 --> 02:53.713
I don't have a right ascension
or descension,

02:53.756 --> 02:57.543
but we can't be too many klicks
off the Galveston coast.

02:57.586 --> 02:59.197
How about I take a deep breath
before I spin?

02:59.240 --> 03:00.459
Put me
out of my misery.

03:00.502 --> 03:02.678
[Chuckles]
No mercy.

03:02.722 --> 03:09.163
