♪ I've been for a walk♪

03:21.001 --> 03:23.133
♪ I've been for a walk♪

03:23.177 --> 03:25.310
♪ On a winter's day♪

03:25.353 --> 03:27.964
♪ On a winter's day♪

03:28.008 --> 03:29.357
♪ If I didn't tell her♪

03:29.401 --> 03:32.186
Leave this here radio on
during daylight.

03:32.230 --> 03:34.101
♪ I could leave today♪

03:34.144 --> 03:36.277
At least what we think
is daylight.

03:36.321 --> 03:40.107
So, if anybody's out there,
just...

03:40.150 --> 03:42.370
you give us a holler.

03:42.414 --> 03:44.894
♪ California dreamin'♪

03:44.938 --> 03:46.592
♪ On such a winter's day♪

03:46.635 --> 03:48.463
♪ California dreamin'♪

